title: Venky Gives Nod to Two projects?
text:
Email 0 
Having gone off the radar for the past few months, actor Venkatesh will soon be back on screen and already has a couple of projects lined up under the Suresh Productions banner, reveal sources. 
After Gopala Gopala released in early January, Venkatesh has maintained a relatively low profile with no new movies or announcements on any upcoming projects. Sources close to him have now revealed that the actor will be back with two films in 2016. 
“Venkatesh has agreed to two films, one of them will be directed by Kranthi Madhav (Of Malli Malli Idhi Rani Roju fame), and the other will be helmed by Maruthi, who is riding high on the success of Bale Bale Magadivoy. Both films will be produced by Suresh Babu,” revealed a source in the know. Both films are yet to go on floors and an official announcement will be made soon. 
Sources close to the actor however, have explain that talks are still in progress and nothing has been finalised as yet.
